2. Category Images
Style: Focused, clean, high-quality product photography with natural backgrounds.

Indoor Plants: "A healthy, vibrant Monstera plant in a stylish white ceramic pot, placed on a wooden stand. Soft interior background, bright natural light. Focus on the glossy split leaves."
Outdoor Plants: "A blooming Rose bush or Hydrangea in a large terracotta planter, placed on a garden patio. Sunlight filtering through leaves. Outdoor garden background."
Succulents: "A group of 3 diverse succulents (Echeveria, Jade, Aloe) in matching small concrete pots. Arranged on a marble surface. Minimalist, clean look."
Flowering Plants: "A stunning Peace Lily or Orchid in bloom, placed on a side table. Soft, elegant lighting. Focus on the delicate flowers and contrast with green leaves."
Herbs: "Fresh, bushy Basil and Rosemary plants in rustic clay pots on a kitchen windowsill. Sunlight streaming in. Culinary herb garden vibe."
